                WS-TEXTO

     MOVE 'TESTE LUCAS' TO WS-TEXTO

     STRING
     WS-TEXTO(7:11)
     WS-TEXTO(1:6)
     DELIMITED BY SIZE INTO WS-CONTEUDO
     END-STRING

    DISPLAY WS-TEXTO
    STOP RUN.
